-- 180-backfill-per-store-course-image-url.sql
--
-- Backfill per-store course_image_url EAV rows for products that are on
-- a country website (MY/GH/NG/BT/IN) but had no store-scoped row at the
-- corresponding store_id — they were silently falling back to the
-- scope-0 default. Magento renders the admin Edit Course > Course
-- Images tab using the store-scoped value, so on country tabs the
-- preview was blank even when scope-0 had a perfectly good URL.
--
-- Fix is a 1:1 mirror of scope-0 into the missing per-store rows.
-- Values are mostly the SG production CDN (tertiarycourses.com.sg)
-- and a handful of R2 bucket URLs; both are public and resolve from
-- any country storefront.
--
-- Generated 2026-05-29 from local DB (~638 rows across 5 country stores).
-- Idempotent: INSERT IGNORE skips rows where the (entity_id,
-- attribute_id, store_id) unique key already exists, so it never
-- overwrites a per-store URL the prod admin uploaded later.

